sources.title: Western Movie | Showdown (1960) | Michael Landon, Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts | Bonanza
sources.description:
Sam Kriby, a young bank robber, gets a job with the Cartwrights in an attempt to prevent the Sheriff from learning the whereabouts of his accomplices the feared Pardo gang.
 
Director: Lewis Allen
Writer: Dean Riesner
Stars: Michael Landon, Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
